<area shape="rect" id="node8" href="#randomNumbers.QuasiRandomUniformPointSet" target="_top" title="Constructor for rendering a quai random point set of dimension *s* and max denominateor *n* which is *fully projection regular* in the $s$&#45;dimensional real&#45;valued [0,1]^s hypercube. The lattice constructor uses a randomly shuffled *uniform* series for the point construction. The resulting point set is stored in a self.pointSet attribute and saved by default in a CSV formatted file." alt="" coords="283,104,485,129"/>
